{
  "texts": [
    "The current study's results affirmed the positive influence of system updates on both knowledge acquisition and application, echoing the findings of previous research 38, 40, 42.",
    "This is indicative of the fact that when Chat-GPT, as an AI language model, receives system updates, it enhances its capabilities to provide more accurate and extensive information, hence positively impacting the users' ability to acquire new knowledge.",
    "Moreover, system updates also seem to have a positive effect on knowledge application.",
    "As the system upgrades, it may introduce new features or improved ways of interacting with the information.",
    "For instance, new tools for organizing, filtering, or visualizing data can enhance users' ability to apply the knowledge they acquired."
  ]
}